  "title": "Website design",
  "body": "Some of those we may or may not want to fix them, just using the website and writing what seems missing.\r\n- [x] No hover effect on any link in header\r\n- [x] Website width is still very narrow compared to https://community.algolia.com/wordpress/customize-autocomplete.html\r\n- [x] Some width break points have no left navigation showing, and you cannot access it\r\n- [x] Hover effect on nav triggers line breaks if length is close to limit <details>![nav](https://cloud.githubusercontent.com/assets/123822/20346414/254c4446-abfc-11e6-923e-b7f9e596eca2.gif)</details>\r\n- [x] Every first line of code snippets has a indent on it <details>![2016-11-16-125028_503x51_scrot](https://cloud.githubusercontent.com/assets/123822/20346227/4977d0de-abfb-11e6-8889-a934edfd4120.png)</details>\r\n- [x] Examples page title is \"examples introduction\" should just be \"examples\"\r\n- [x] Examples page should be designed a bit, a simple page showing screenshots as squares would do it (no need for examples introduction page)\r\n- [x] Left nav issue (browser width: 624px)<details>![leftnav](https://cloud.githubusercontent.com/assets/123822/20346557/09e3307e-abfd-11e6-8ca9-a3da16361bee.gif)</details>\r\n- [x] Full width API navigation dropdown can't be closed when clicking away\r\n- [x] big atom logo does not scale with breakpoints, example: <details>![](https://cloud.githubusercontent.com/assets/123822/20347209/5373e564-ac00-11e6-8966-c56238035e31.png)</details>\r\n- [ ] Left nav issue when going from small window to big window (left nav is messed up)<details>![2016-11-16-130411_1382x787_scrot](https://cloud.githubusercontent.com/assets/123822/20346587/320b8f06-abfd-11e6-986e-405ca5cab310.png)</details>\r\n----- \r\n\r\n- [ ] Properly indent code sample <details>![](https://puu.sh/sl9KS/8d3f59161d.png)</details>\r\n\r\n----- \r\n### done \r\n```diff\r\n- No hover effect on any link in header\r\n- Website width is still very narrow compared to \r\n- Some width break points have no left navigation showing, and you cannot access it\r\n- Hover effect on nav triggers line breaks if length is close to limit\r\n- Every first line of code snippets has a indent on it\r\n- Examples page title is \"examples introduction\" should just be \"examples\"\r\n- Examples page should be designed a bit, a simple page showing screenshots as squares would do it (no need for examples introduction page)\r\n- Left nav issue (browser width: 624px)\r\n- Full width API navigation dropdown can't be closed when clicking away\r\n- Big atom logo does not scale with breakpoints\r\n```\r\n\r\n\r\n### doing \r\n\r\n```diff\r\n+  Left nav issue when going from small window to big window (left nav is messed up)\r\n````\r\n\r\n<p align=\"center\">\r\n  <b>⚡️ Incoming Awesomeness ⚡️</b>\r\n</p>",
